Mojave …2004 oil on canvas 
I’ve been traveling to the Mojave Desert for 50 years and have been drawn to the vast emptiness and many shades of rust that colors the landscape. This painting I entitled, Mojave was inspired by my visits to Joshua Tree in 2004.
